cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and machine learning, specifically on visual object tracking in videos using deep reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves decision-making processes, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the paper uses neural networks, which could also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
